rows.label: qst200501_0010
rows.name:
What is it you hope to achieve
with this fire, Yuou?

rows.label: qst200501_0030
rows.name:
To burn the stuff we've
collected, of course!

rows.label: qst200501_0040
rows.name:
Seems a bit of a waste
to burn all of this...

rows.label: qst200501_0070
rows.name:
Aligo are attracted by smells
you know. It's a funny thing.

rows.label: qst200501_0080
rows.name:
If we make skillful use of this, we
can get them to come over here...

rows.label: qst200501_0100
rows.name:
Indeed, the things that we
gathered earlier are giving
off a certain odor.

rows.label: qst200501_0110
rows.name:
If the smell starts to waft
over their way, they'll
probably come over this way.

rows.label: qst200501_0120
rows.name:
If we play it right, we can
collect up the cargo without
having to fight them.

rows.label: qst200501_0130
rows.name: Mo... That really enough to bring them?

rows.label: qst200501_0140
rows.name:
It's fine, it's fine. I
know what I'm doing.

rows.label: qst200501_0150
rows.name:
Now, let's find a good vantage
point to watch the action unfold!

rows.label: qst200501_0170
rows.name:
Well, maybe we didn't get all of
them. But it'll be a lot easier
to collect what we need now.

rows.label: qst200501_0180
rows.name: Wow! Yuou a very dependable chap!

rows.label: qst200501_0190
rows.name:
Well, thanks! But y'know, I'm
just doing my regular thing!
